Package: DefenseViz
Title: Restriction-Modification System Analysis and Visualization Pipeline
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Jae-Yoon", "Sung", email = "o3wodbs@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A comprehensive R package for analyzing Restriction-Modification (R-M) 
    systems from DNMB output. Features include methylation motif extraction, 
    nuclease activity prediction, operon structure analysis, TRD domain extraction, 
    REBASE database comparison, and integrated scoring system.
